('affiliates', 'Affiliates &amp; Links', '        &lt;p&gt;The following websites are provided as a resource for our referring doctors. This page contains hyperlinks to World Wide Web sites that are created and maintained by other organizations. We have included these links because we think that our referring doctors may find them of interest. Keep in mind that Dr. Cook does not necessarily endorse the views expressed on these websites. Also, we do not guarantee the accuracy or completeness of any information presented on these sites.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;h2&gt;Periodontist Links&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.distraction.net&quot;&gt;Alveolar Distraction Osteogenesis&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.perio.org/index.html&quot;&gt;American Academy of Periodontology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.perio.org/links/links.html&quot;&gt;American Academy of Periodontists Links Page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.perio.org/amboard/amboard.html&quot;&gt;American Board of Periodontology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.icoi.org&quot;&gt;International Congress of Oral Implantologists (ICOI)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;h2&gt;Dental Implant Links:&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.3implant.com&quot;&gt;3i (Implant Innovations, Inc.)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.osseo.org&quot;&gt;Academy of Osseointegration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bicon.com&quot;&gt;Bicon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ICOI.org&quot;&gt;International Congress of Oral Implantology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nobelbiocare.com&quot;&gt;Nobel Biocare&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.straumann.com&quot;&gt;Straumann&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.calcitek.com&quot;&gt;Zimmer Dental&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n        &lt;h2&gt;Hygenist Links&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bdha.org.uk/bdhahome/proforg.cfm&quot;&gt;British Dental Hygienists&#039; Association&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.toothfairy.org&quot;&gt;The Tooth Fairy Homepage&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wku.edu/AHHS/dhpge.htm&quot;&gt;Dental Hygiene Homepage: WKU on Line&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;h2&gt;Women&Atilde;ƒ&Acirc;&cent;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;s Health Links&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.4woman.org&quot;&gt;National Women&Atilde;ƒ&Acirc;&cent;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;s Health Information Center&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.womens-health.com&quot;&gt;Women&Atilde;ƒ&Acirc;&cent;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;s Health Interactive&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.AMA.Assn.org/special/womh.htm&quot;&gt;Journal of the American Medical Assoc. Women&Atilde;ƒ&Acirc;&cent;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;s Health&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.health.harvard.edu&quot;&gt;Harvard Women&Atilde;ƒ&Acirc;&cent;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;&Atilde;&macr;&Acirc;&iquest;&Acirc;&frac12;s Health Watch&lt;/a&gt;');
